        "header_type": "left",
        "heading": "<h2>67 layers of Damascus, classic design</h2>",
        "content": "<p>The Yi Series pairs a 10Cr15CoMoV core with 67 layers of Damascus cladding at 60 HRC. The same proven steel found across Xinzuo's premium Damascus range, wrapped in a classic rosewood handle that honours traditional knife-making aesthetics.</p>",
        "icon_block_state": true,
